➜凤萍（香港）：爱你！一种流泪的幸福
http://www.sohu.com/a/415652907_100115135	47106
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200830/4f686a388d1b45c285e68e1545e0466f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爱你！一种流泪的幸福</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/凤萍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫步你我牵手的街道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">影子留在熟悉的小巷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想你，泪与秋风纠结</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与落叶相伴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>思念爬上经年的枝蔓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>岁月柔情是你的存在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>剪一段思念，在水的中央</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>追逐你必经的路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眸子沿着思念的藤蔓而去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手托起飘落的泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像一个疯子自言自语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像一抹空气亲吻着你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沉思</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>望月吟唱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一种流泪的幸福</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>呢喃岁月的斑斓</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">月光洒落一地的想念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沉陷你我的灵魂里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是你我千年张望的方向</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想你，一种穿透心扉的惆怅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱你，有一种眼睛含沙的痛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爱你！把爱堆集成佛缘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>经年绽放成莲花</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蜻蜒是你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我在莲下游戏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>与你缠绵相望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落叶惊醒婆娑的回忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念托秋风寄予鸿雁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我的诗篇写着你的世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你的情深写进我的诗里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>捡片落叶装入行囊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>装满整个秋季的风景</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>嵌入笔下的纸笺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迤逦成爱你的诗行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.08.30凌晨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200830/72d7e6d0554b44ca8a55fc72ef597b89.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>凤萍，原名戴凤萍，原籍江西，现居香港。中、西医营养师；从事产前、产后饮食营养和产后护理工作；幼儿早期教育。作品散见海内外纸媒和网媒。</p>
<p><strong>诗观：持一颗初心，写心中情感！爱与诗同行！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200830/5c15ae1d82bb429eaed2e6a2f59a6193.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
