➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：渡口
http://www.sohu.com/a/415652072_100115135	47220
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200830/3cf40cc32fdc4e1d8dfa88160d72548a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渡口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸福快乐,像一片云飘过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四年路程诀别一个驿站</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风尘仆仆的青春赶不上又启程的船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一只手提箱打包带走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份感情空落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眉头驮着重重的云雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳枝挥着风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挂着泪点,一尾浪翻腾着忧伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无力挥别在渡口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他的初恋乘船已走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年8月29日晚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200830/d617f53f1cfb46abaa129553d48ccfac.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
